Package busy.company.web

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CompanyController
    Controller for Company operations, like create or filter by category or name.
    CompanyForm
    Form model to handle the POST request for registering a new company.
    OnRegisterCompany
    Event for a performed registration of a company.
    OnUpdateCompanyStatus
    Event for a performed update of company status.
    RegisterCompanyListener
    Application listener called when a company registration is performed.
    RegisterCompanyValidator
    New company Form Validator.
    UpdateCompanyStatusListener
    Application listener called when an status update of a company is performed.
